{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154680/extras/Can_you_find_the_light.gif?t=1603235487\" /><br><br>You play as Ogden, an orphan whose curiosity got the better of him. After disobeying the headmistress of his orphanage and sneaking into a locked room, he gave in to temptation and tried on a cursed mask that transformed him into a monster. You will have to get used to this new body, master monstrous abilities, and try not to lose the last remnants of your humanity. You have the advantages of bestial agility, monstrous strength, and inhuman capabilities. But watch out \u2014 in this hostile world, almost everything is out to get you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154680/extras/Explore.gif?t=1603235487\" /><br>The world of The Guise is filled with terrifying locations, including dying villages, dark forests, labyrinthine dungeons, and deadly valleys swarming with demons. Find secrets, hidden passageways, and concealed rooms containing treasures that shed new light on Ogden's world.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154680/extras/take_advantage.gif?t=1603235487\" /><br>The main gameplay hook is your persistent monstrous form. As a human, you could have fought with a sword or any other weapon, but now you have only your newfound feral abilities to rely on.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154680/extras/Evolve_1.gif?t=1603235487\" /><br>Unlock new monstrous abilities by defeating bosses and absorbing their skills. Every time you vanquish an ordinary foe, you collect their eyeballs \u2014 local currency that can be spent to upgrade your abilities with the Eye Collector.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154680/extras/Seek_the_light.gif?t=1603235487\" /><br>The macabre world of The Guise may be harsh and unjust, but there are still a few people you can count on - for example, children whose eyes remain unsullied, whose perception of the world has yet to be touched by the darkness. Or the Eye Collector, who keenly senses the pain and despair of this boy trapped in the body of a monster.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fiend of the Old World","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/8e1240edef06df5ad7ee16d58b0d1047227b871e.jpg"},{"name":"Witch of the Sunken Village","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/727a9a084a4aac69f8d39649e52060a55f3548d9.jpg"},{"name":"Queen of the Rats","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/9d8ee0bddde40c5e87e45381e14c8b7e4c5814df.jpg"},{"name":"Beast of the Depths","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/1ac65592ffbe72e836c08c893a451f29d7d55783.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Princess","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/2e4799399fa216552f4a832cafe108ef8ff21e1d.jpg"},{"name":"Gravedigger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/d3d013cb3d78f06f5ea20b3e21dc02095549fbd6.jpg"},{"name":"Mayor of Gooseville","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/19deb84245043ff70814891acf08158960838a57.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Prince","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/be4eb112109dfff47dc12546e8ce168bc93dcace.jpg"},{"name":"Imprisoned Mortal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/a9c6e3afc67041a7ae8a1a2728e01f4d80705ce9.jpg"},{"name":"End of the Road","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1154680/3f7f2671a9b3d546edc0aad67a04093e05483